Suggests: default-mysql-server, php-ldap
Description: IP Address Management (IPAM) system
 OpenNetAdmin provides a database managed inventory of your IP network.
 Each subnet, host, and IP can be tracked via a centralized AJAX enabled web
 interface that can help reduce tracking errors.
 .
 A full CLI interface is available as well to use for scripting and bulk work.
